<text>
   <body>
      <div type="original">
         <div rend="head" style="letter">
            <p>Gentoftegade 14. Gentofte Tlf. Gentofte 144</p>
         </div>
         <div rend="body">
            <p>Hr. <persName key="hoyerNiels">Niels Hoyer</persName></p>
            <p><placeName>Havnegade</placeName> 47 <placeName key="copenhagen"
               >København</placeName></p>
            <p>Efter Aftale med <persName key="lili">Fru Lili Elvenes</persName> sender jeg Dem
               hermed et Billede (som jeg gerne ønsker <hi rend="underline">retur</hi>, da det er
               det eneste, jeg ejer) af min Svoger Kunstmaler <persName key="wegenerE">Einar
                  Wegener</persName>.</p>
            <p>Jeg beder Dem tale med mig <hi rend="underline">inden</hi> De sender noget uddrag af
               Manuskriptet til <placeName key="germany">Tyskland</placeName> – min Telefon er efter
               6.30 Gentofte 144, og i Løbet af Dagen er det : Central 4726.</p>

            <p>Med megen Agtelse</p>
            <signed>
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <persName key="thomsenTC">TC Thomsen</persName>
               </hi>
            </signed>

            <postscript>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="underline">Ingeniør</hi>
               </p>
            </postscript>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div type="translation">
         <div rend="head" style="letter">
            <p>Gentoftegade 14. Gentofte Tel. Gentofte 144</p>
         </div>
         <div rend="body">
            <p>Sir. <persName key="hoyerNiels">Niels Hoyer</persName></p>
            <p><placeName>Harbor Street</placeName> 47 <placeName key="copenhagen"
                  >Copenhagan</placeName></p>
            <p>As agreed with <persName key="lili">Mrs. Lili Elvenes</persName> I hereby send you a
               picture (which I would like you to <hi rend="underline">return</hi> as it is the only
               one I own) of my brother-in-law painter <persName key="wegenerE">Einar
                  Wegener</persName>.</p>
            <p>I ask you to talk to me <hi rend="underline">before</hi> sending any transcript of
               the manuscript to <placeName key="germany">Germany</placeName> – my telephone number
               after 6:30 is Gentofte 144, and during the day it is : Central 4726.</p>

            <p>With much respect</p>
            <signed>
               <hi rend="underline">
                  <persName key="thomsenTC">TC Thomsen</persName>
               </hi>
            </signed>

            <postscript>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="underline">Engineer</hi>
               </p>
            </postscript>
         </div>
      </div>
   </body>
</text>
